  "title": "All-Party Parliamentary Group on Industrial Strategy",
  "purpose": "To facilitate cross-party dialogue on the UK's new industrial strategy. The APPG aims to provide a forum for government, businesses and other stakeholders to exchange knowledge of the strategy as it is developed and to ensure it works for all parts of the country.",
